{"tid":2114962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許樹昌：疫情已滲透全港　政府有必要帶頭讓公務員在家工作","createTime":"2020-07-19T07:52:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T08:59:55.000Z","uid":7542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44d2deb6af0d698403616c6a7c2452f96cc84f11","tid":2114962,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:52:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>政府有必要帶頭中計！</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【有線新聞】政府委任的專家許樹昌形容疫情已滲透全港，不明源頭個案增加令人擔心，而上星期收緊措施亦未必有效應付這一波，政府有必要帶頭公務員在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n第三波疫情由兩星期前的彬記茶餐廳開始之後，陸續出現不同群組，最多是港泰護老中心，彬記、新發等茶餐廳群組亦超過40人確診，還有慈雲山中心，單是翠河及薀莎餐廳亦都超過40人確診。<br />\n<br />\n看回數據本地感染個案近一星期持續急升，上星期四有63宗，更令人擔心是這一波疫情，不明源頭的個案佔四成。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌：「病毒傳播性高了三四倍，好明顯沒有症狀的人入社區，更難找到源頭。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30708&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=bda4c7a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30708&h=0616a5e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30708</a>"},{"pid":"cbf721e316b3bc0bd7ffdedf3d154e3b76241326","tid":2114962,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>有邊間公司無中計一齊整個 List: </strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正苦"},{"pid":"4dffae0d77735c2d02be41433bfd4422f1673b47","tid":2114962,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbf721e316b3bc0bd7ffdedf3d154e3b76241326","tid":2114962,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>有邊間公司無中計一齊整個 List: </strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<